summary: Decided to redraw a character I made in early 2015 and also try out something new. This is Chalcedony Dentritic Agate, who I...
caption: Decided to redraw a character I made in early 2015 and also try out something new. This is Chalcedony Dentritic Agate, who I decided to use for my first attempt at a reference sheet. In her original design she would have had freckles on the arms, neck and cheeks. I decided to go for stripes this time, as it would be easier to recreate in any future images. If anyone has any tips to help further improve, I’d love to hear them.
